'''Ḥaleb''' (neɣ s [[taɛrabt]] : ''ﺣﻠﺐ'', ''Halep'' s [[taṭerkit]]) d tamdint n ugafa n [[Surya]], nettat ay d tamdint yugaren tiyaḍ di tmurt-nni, zedɣen-tt 2,132,100 n yimezdaɣen di [[2004]] sdat  [[Amagaru aɣarim asuri|Wemagaru aɣarim asuri]].
Naqal di tmiḍi tis 20, llant deg-s tigrawin tintin am [[Aɛraben|Waɛraben]], [[Iṭerkmanen]], [[Ikurdiyen]],, [[Acuriyen]] (Isuryanen) , [[Arminiyen]], [[Ičerkesen]], [[Udayen]] ed [[Igrikiyen]]
Yerna Ḥaleb tettwasnen s [[Taqṣebt n Ḥaleb|Teqṣebt]]-is ed uṣabun-is. 


